phpPgAdmin CrudGen Plugin Installation Guide
-------------------------------------------
1. CrudGen Plugin activation

   Open conf/config.inc.php and add the 'CrudGen' value in the $conf['plugins'] array:

   $conf['plugins'] = array('CrudGen');

2. Set up the CrudGen database.

   If you want to enable CrudGen (which are a useful feature for creating CRUD pages in minutes)
   then go to the 'sql' subdirectory and view the SQL script for your database.  It
   will contain instructions on how to set up the CrudGen database.
